propel.core.collections.lists.primitive

Class LongArrayList

  • java.lang.Object
    • propel.core.collections.lists.primitive.LongArrayList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ILongArrayList

    public class LongArrayList
extends java.lang.Object
implements ILongArrayList
    A primitive long array-backed list that uses similar semantics and strategy to the java.util.ArrayList.

        public long[] toArray(long[] a)
